 of the american embassy in panama the commercial service an agency within the us department of commerce’s international trade administration is the frontline agency for the execution of the us government’s national export initiative nei and its successor neinext our mission is to help us companies export goods and services made in the us to develop and protect us business interests in panama to help us firms resolve market barriers and to promote panamanian investment into the united states we have a vast network at our fingertips supported by more than  international industry and trade specialists whose job it is to provide the best source of customized solutions for us companies and their panamanian partners to do business in the global marketplace whether you’re a us company looking for an export opportunity or a panamanian firm looking for new suppliers in the us you’ve come to the right place new business is waiting for you welcome to panama want an example we helped rotec industries from chicago win a  million contract for the panama canal expansion project see their story here httpwwwyoutubecomwatchviqfdpjis we hope you will take a moment to look at our website and familiarize yourself with the variety of opportunities tailored programs and customized services available to you through our office in panama then you can contact us we also encourage you to contact a us  based export assistance center where trade specialists will provide you with guidance on entering panama and other exciting international markets please visit httpexportgovusofficesindexasp to locate the office nearest you follow us on twitter  panamauscs our global network at work find your next export market in the international trade administrations top markets series reports see the list of newly announced  international buyer program trade shows   print  last updated   am how to export ecommerce export education finding foreign markets legal considerations logistics financial considerations