 spin there are so many rainforests to hike volcanic peaks to climb coral reefs to scuba dive and theres so much colonial splendor to see that you cant possibly see and do everything that central america has to offer in one trip you can certainly make a good go of it though the best of central america the most unforgettable travel experiences best dining bets the best outdoor adventures best hotel bets the best websites the best beaches the best museums  churches the best markets the best small towns and villages the most intriguing historical sites countries belize costa rica el salvador guatemala honduras nicaragua panama regions atlantic lowlands balsamo coast bambito cerro punta and guadelupe caribbean nicaragua central guatemala central pacific costa rica central panama comarca kuna yala costa ricas caribbean coast costa ricas southern zone darien province eastern comarca kuna yala eastern el salvador eastern pacific el salvador gamboa and the canal zone guanacaste and the nicoya peninsula honduras north coast la mosquitia lake atitlan lake atitlan villages le peninsula de azuero los pueblos blancos malpais and santa teresa north central el salvador north central nicaragua northern belize northern cayes and atolls northern costa rica northwest el salvador olancho orosi valley outside panama city pacific beaches pacific coast pacific el salvador peten playa del coco and playa ocotal playa grande playas brasilito and conchal rio bravo conservation area rio san juan ruta de las flores san jose central valley southern belize southern honduras southwest nicaragua volcanic lowlands western belize western cocle province western comarca kuna yala western el salvador western highlands western honduras western panama cities alajuela poas  the airport area alegria antigua guatemala barra de santiago barra del colorado belize city belmopan bluefields boquete brus laguna cahuita cartago catacamas chichicastenango choluteca coban colon comayagua concepcion de quezaltepeque c